		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You place a drop of bile from a &amp;reference[giant] slug on your tongue and spit. Acidic sludge manifests around your enemy, coating them in disgusting &amp;reference[ooze].</em></p><p><strong>[[/save dex]]{Dexterity Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> [[/damage]] immediately and [[/damage activity=vNvHHSA1d8gj8rA8]] at the end of target's next turn.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half initial damage, no other effect.</p></li></ul><p><em><strong>Upcasting:</strong></em> Increase initial damage by [[/damage 2d4 acid]] for each slot level above 4th.</p>",
